It is an enchanted, anti-good, and anti-neutral piece of clothing.
It increases defensive bonus by two and decreases saving spell by ten.
It weighs one pound and twelve ounces, and it is worth about 33 gold and 15 silver.
Its keywords are robe and pitch-black.
Its magical key is khaegoeroc.
It returns mana after a short period of time when casting certain spells. This effect does not stack for
multiple uses of the same spell, but can be active for several spells at the same time.
